										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<span class="span-reading-time rt-reading-time" style="display: block;"><span class="rt-label rt-prefix">Reading Time: </span> <span class="rt-time"> 4</span> <span class="rt-label rt-postfix">minutes</span></span>
<p>Have Meghan Markle and Prince Harry been snubbed by the Clooneys?</p>



<p><a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2023/01/meghan-markle-vs-kate-middleton-tailor-comes-forward-with-final-word-on-infamous-wedding-dress-feud/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Meghan and Harry&#8217;s 2018 wedding</a> was the social event of the year, with A-list stars and dignitaries from across the globe in attendance.</p>



<p>Among the celebrities on hand were George and Amal Clooney, who had developed a close friendship with the Sussexes in the months after they announced their engagement.</p>



<p>Unfortunately, it seems that the two couples have drifted apart in recent years.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="684" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-1024x684.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-485539" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-768x513.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-2048x1367.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-735x491.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-335x224.jpg 335w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-347x232.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-520x347.jpg 520w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-960x641.jpg 960w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-531017112-1080x721.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">George Clooney and his wife Amal Clooney attend the &#8220;Money Monster&#8221; premiere during the 69th annual Cannes Film Festival at the Palais des Festivals on May 12, 2016 in Cannes, France.<span class="image-caption-credit"> (Getty Images)</span></figcaption></figure>



<p>Perhaps it&#8217;s the fact that they now live on separate continents, or maybe there was some sort of secret falling out.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-harry-and-meghan-vs-the-clooneys">Harry and Meghan vs. the Clooneys</h2>



<p>For unknown reasons, the Clooneys allegedly failed to invite Harry and Meghan to the third annual Albie Awards.</p>



<p>The Clooney Foundation for Justice in New York City hosted the star-studded event in September of 2024.</p>



<p>George and Amal left the couple off the guest list despite the fact that <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2024/08/prince-harry-prince-williams-nyc-run-in/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Harry was in Manhattan</a> that week to attend the Clinton Global Initiative Summit. In other words, he easily could&#8217;ve attended.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="787" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-1024x787.jpg" alt="Meghan, Duchess of Sussex and Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex attend the 2022 Robert F. Kennedy Human Rights Ripple of Hope Gala at New York Hilton on December 06, 2022 in New York City." class="wp-image-510685" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-300x230.jpg 300w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-768x590.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-2048x1573.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-960x737.jpg 960w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-1080x830.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1447258326-2-1200x922.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Meghan, Duchess of Sussex and Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex attend the 2022 Robert F. Kennedy Human Rights Ripple of Hope Gala at New York Hilton on December 06, 2022 in New York City.<span class="image-caption-credit"> (Photo by Mike Coppola/Getty Images for 2022 Robert F. Kennedy Human Rights Ripple of Hope Gala)</span></figcaption></figure>



<p></p>



<p>And it&#8217;s worth noting that this was the second straight year the duke and duchess were MIA at the event.</p>



<p>Sources say the Sussexes were stunned when the Clooneys didn&#8217;t invite them to the star-studded soiree in 2023.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-george-and-amal-execute-a-royal-diss">George and Amal Execute a Royal Diss</h2>



<p>&#8220;Of all the snubs they&#8217;ve had to deal with since their move to Hollywood, this is probably the most hurtful [to Harry and Meghan],&#8221; one insider told the <em>National Enquirer</em> (<a href="https://radaronline.com/p/prince-harry-meghan-markle-humiliated-snubbed-george-amal-gala/">via</a> Radar Online). </p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="683" height="1024" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-683x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-483912" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-200x300.jpg 200w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-735x1103.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-223x335.jpg 223w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-231x347.jpg 231w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-347x520.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-427x640.jpg 427w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-512x768.jpg 512w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-640x960.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1678303308-scaled.jpg 1706w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex and Meghan, Duchess of Sussex attend the Wheelchair Basketball preliminary match between Ukraine and Australia during day four of the Invictus Games DÃ¼sseldorf 2023 on September 13, 2023 in Dusseldorf, Germany. <span class="image-caption-credit"> (Photo Credit: Getty Images)</span></figcaption></figure>



<p>&#8220;George and Amal went from being their wedding guests and trusted confidants to totally ghosting them.&#8221;</p>



<p>As an actress, <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2023/10/meghan-markle-was-humiliated-by-spotify-firing-insider-claims/">Meghan likely encountered her fair share of rejection</a>, but this sort of snub is probably new to Harry.</p>



<p>And it seems that the Sussexes are not taking it well.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="720" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-1024x720.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-483901" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-1024x720.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-300x211.jpg 300w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-768x540.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-1536x1080.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-2048x1440.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-735x517.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-335x236.jpg 335w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-347x244.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-520x366.jpg 520w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-640x450.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-960x675.jpg 960w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1682251014-1080x760.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex and Meghan, Duchess of Sussex attend the cycling medal ceremony at the Cycling Track during day six of the Invictus Games DÃ¼sseldorf 2023 on September 15, 2023 in Dusseldorf, Germany. <span class="image-caption-credit"> (Photo Credit: Getty Images)</span></figcaption></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-harry-and-meghan-left-reeling">Harry and Meghan Left Reeling</h2>



<p>&#8220;It&#8217;s a huge kick in the teeth and a massive embarrassment they can&#8217;t really explain or wrap their heads around,&#8221; the insider added.</p>



<p>&#8220;The gala would have been a dream event for the two, but George and Amal knew only too well the circus that follows them would have ruined it for others.&#8221;</p>



<p>Yes, the first snub came at a time when <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2023/10/meghan-markle-is-strategizing-her-hollywood-reinvention-with-a-new-pr-team-is-the-duchess-getting-desperate-for-a-comeback/">Harry and Meghan were attempting to rebuild their public image</a> following a string of bad press.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="683" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-1024x683.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-483640" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-735x490.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-335x223.jpg 335w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-347x231.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-520x347.jpg 520w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-960x640.jpg 960w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/09/GettyImages-1680320928-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex and Meghan, Duchess of Sussex meet with NATO Joint Force Command and families from Italy and Netherlands during day five of the Invictus Games DÃ¼sseldorf 2023 on September 14, 2023 in Duesseldorf, Germany. <span class="image-caption-credit"> (Photo Credit: Getty Images)</span></figcaption></figure>



<p>Being spotted at an A-list charity event would&#8217;ve provided exactly the sort of boost that Harry and Meghan needed to help them reclaim their place at the top of the global celebrity totem pole.</p>



<p>The situation comes as a shock, as the Clooneys previously spoke quite highly of the Sussexes.</p>



<p>&#8220;We live not too far from one another and we have dinners and stuff and we&#8217;re friends with them for all the reasons that you&#8217;re friends with anybody,&#8221; George told the <em>Daily Mail</em> in 2020.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="683" height="1024" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-683x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-485544" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-200x300.jpg 200w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-735x1103.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-223x335.jpg 223w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-231x347.jpg 231w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-347x520.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-427x640.jpg 427w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-512x768.jpg 512w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-640x960.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2023/10/GettyImages-1427021761-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Amal Clooney and George Clooney attend HISTORYTalks 2022 on September 24, 2022 in Washington, DC. <span class="image-caption-credit"> (Getty Images)</span></figcaption></figure>



<p>&#8220;They&#8217;re just really nice, fun, kind people, they&#8217;re a very loving couple, and they&#8217;re going to be great parents.&#8221;</p>



<p>We may never know exactly what caused the two couples to drift apart.</p>



<p>But with <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2024/06/george-clooney-divorce-actor-and-wife-living-separate-lives-source-claims/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">divorce rumors circulating around George and Amal</a>, the Clooneys might have decided to shrink their social circle in an effort to sidestep unnecessary drama.</p>



<p>And it&#8217;s possible that as UK residents, George and Amal have decided that their loyalty lies with the Windsors.</p>



